[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0309","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0309.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0125","title":"Wired Community Software WWWThreads 5.0 SQL注入漏洞","description":"WWWThreads 5.0 论坛系统存在 SQL 注入漏洞，由于程序未对传递给 SQL 查询的数值类型数据及表名进行有效过滤，远程攻击者可通过构造特制的 SQL 命令输入，绕过身份验证机制，实现对论坛数据库的任意操作，包括窃取用户凭证、篡改论坛内容或提升管理员权限。该漏洞影响 Wired Community Software WWWThreads 5.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0125"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:03.143","remediation":"立即升级 WWWThreads 至 5.0 以上最新版本，该版本已修复 SQL 注入问题。如厂商已停止维护，建议迁移至其他受支持的论坛系统（如 phpBB、Discourse）。临时缓解措施：在 Web 应用层对所有用户输入（包括数字参数和表名参数）实施严格的类型校验和参数化查询，禁止将用户输入直接拼接至 SQL 语句。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/967","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.4.10.10002031027120.15921-100000%40eight.wiretrip.net","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19741","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8de487bef2c8b1936da1237463dc6052a1fcd655/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0125.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0125","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0125.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/263f37bc67cd24fe03a39077d8b57f3001369a95/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0125.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vmr6-rxwm-662f/GHSA-vmr6-rxwm-662f.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0125.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001150.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0309.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0115","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0115.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0127","title":"Webspeed 权限提升漏洞","description":"Progress WebSpeed配置程序未正确禁用对WSMadmin实用程序的访问控制，远程攻击者可通过调用wsisa.dll组件绕过权限限制，从而获得系统提升权限。该漏洞影响Progress WebSpeed应用服务器相关版本，CVSS评分7.5分（高危），攻击者无需认证即可远程利用wsisa.dll漏洞获取系统提升权限，Progress Software已发布补丁修复该权限提升漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0127"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:03.400","remediation":"建议升级到 Webspeed 厂商发布的修复版本（4.1 及以上），并通过 Web 服务器配置禁用对 wsisa.dll 及 WSMadmin 实用程序的远程访问，将相关 CGI/ISAPI 路径限制为仅本地回环地址访问；同时在边界防火墙或反向代理上阻断对 /scripts/wsisa.dll 等路径的外部请求，作为无法立即升级时的临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.progress.com/services/support/cgi-bin/techweb-kbase.cgi/webkb.html?kbid=19412&keywords=security%20Webspeed","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/969","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/37a97bfb1a242345a1cabbc32cd8d143b89d9075/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0127.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0127","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0127.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/be19cdaa6196942fd4096a42a1eaf047a8584298/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0127.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/805.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b1dd20ab76cf8f3afbe611ea8133362b0532868d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g9qx-grqj-38gf/GHSA-g9qx-grqj-38gf.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/webspeed.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0127.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0115.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0115.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0110","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0110.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0122","title":"Microsoft FrontPage Server Extensions htimage.exe 路径泄露漏洞","description":"MS FrontPage服务器扩展中的htimage.exe CGI程序存在路径泄露漏洞。该漏洞允许远程攻击者通过向虚拟目录的htimage.exe程序发送特定的GET请求，获取到服务器的物理文件路径信息。该漏洞影响MS FrontPage服务器及其构建的虚拟目录环境。攻击者无需身份验证即可利用此漏洞，获取敏感的服务器文件路径信息，为进一步攻击提供情报支持，CVSS评分5.0，危害等级中等。该漏洞本质上是FrontPage Server Extensions CGI处理程序对用户输入缺乏有效验证，允许攻击者通过简单HTTP请求获取服务器内部路径信息。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0122"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:02.767","remediation":"升级至 FrontPage 2000 Server Extensions SR-1 及以上版本（含 MS00-057 补丁），或在 IIS 中删除/禁用 _vti_bin/htimage.exe CGI 程序；若无法升级，可配置 URLScan 或 IIS 请求筛选规则拦截含 htimage.exe 的 GET 请求作为临时缓解","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/470458/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/964","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/34719","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d08a5c34806fec51f3d6c8b496ad617d8294f215/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0122.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0122","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0122.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c8b0fec8b23470355b47059dbab5d2ebdfa2ac94/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0122.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-353v-v7pq-8gpc/GHSA-353v-v7pq-8gpc.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/964/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0122.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001148.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0110.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0096","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0096.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0112","title":"Debian GNU/Linux MBR 安全绕过漏洞","description":"Debian GNU/Linux 在默认安装时使用了安全性不足的引导扇区（MBR，主引导记录），该引导记录未对本地启动设备进行足够限制。在系统安装阶段，具备本地物理接触或控制台访问权限的用户可利用此缺陷，在开机时插入软盘并从软盘引导启动系统，从而绕过正常的安装与引导流程及潜在的安全控制。该漏洞影响采用 Debian GNU/Linux 默认安装配置的本地系统，攻击条件为攻击者需拥有对目标机器的本地物理访问权限，利用方式是在安装过程中插入软盘并选择从软盘引导，进而可能干扰或绕过系统安装与后续的安全机制。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0112"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:01.543","remediation":"升级到已修复该问题的 Debian GNU/Linux 2.2 (potato) 及以上版本，安装后使用 lilo 或 grub-install 重新写入受保护的 Master Boot Record。在安装阶段对服务器加设 BIOS 密码并禁用软盘启动（将 BIOS 启动顺序设为仅从硬盘启动），同时对物理控制台实施访问限制，防止本地用户借软盘引导绕过系统安全限制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94973075614088&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/960","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5b55afba6f3a87fe9319e1de76170e4c2760d614/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0112.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0112","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0112.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0112.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-992g-c72f-vm8c/GHSA-992g-c72f-vm8c.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0112.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001146.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ca03f6ab-f187-46e1-8849-8042206df44e.json","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0096.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0001","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0114","title":"Microsoft Frontpage Server Extensions 匿名账户名称泄露漏洞","description":"Frontpage Server Extensions 存在信息泄露漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器 `/_vti_bin/` 虚拟目录下的 `shtml.dll` 发送特制的 RPC POST 请求，利用该漏洞获取服务器上匿名账户的名称。该漏洞影响运行 Microsoft FrontPage Server Extensions 的 IIS 服务器，攻击者无需任何凭据即可在远程发起探测，造成敏感账户信息泄露，为后续攻击提供有利信息。Microsoft 已在后续安全更新中修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0114"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:01.787","remediation":"升级 Microsoft FrontPage Server Extensions 至包含该漏洞修复的 FrontPage 2000 Server Extensions 更新版本（如 Windows 2000 SP1 及以上随附版本），或通过 Windows Update 安装对应安全补丁。临时缓解措施：在 IIS 中移除或限制对 /_vti_bin/ 虚拟目录（尤其是 shtml.dll）的匿名 RPC POST 访问权限，并配置 IP 限制或关闭不必要的 FrontPage 扩展功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0114","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2000/CVE-2000-0114.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/2000/CVE-2000-0114.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/864f48c7816d76393a2caf81508e551068cf8863/2000/CVE-2000-0114.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/832b30ce23760d77f9ea78b30de78b96d425fbe0/http/cves/2000/CVE-2000-0114.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/low/cve-2000-0114-1296.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder4/cve-2000-0114-1297.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2000-0114_3.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0114","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2000-0114-1297.yaml","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/9ddbd359f5d34d4a30a937d3247f869d55e5f670/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-01xx/CVE-2000-0114.json","https://github.com/amad3us47/amad3us47.github.io/blob/14d36cd646300e9b9b8fa1a2222524533239a69b/data/CVE-2000-0114.yaml","https://github.com/Cappricio-Securities/CVE-2000-0114","https://github.com/adhamelhansye/CVE-2000-0114","https://github.com/Josekutty-K/frontpage-server-extensions-vulnerability-scanner"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0001.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0406","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0406.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0136","title":"Cart32/QuickCommerce/Shop Express/StoreCreator 等多款购物车应用隐藏表单字段信息篡改漏洞","description":"Cart32 等多款购物车应用存在隐藏表单字段篡改漏洞。远程攻击者可通过修改 Web 表单中隐藏的价格、数量等敏感字段值，以低于原价的金额完成订单交易，导致商家经济损失。该漏洞影响 Cart32 2.5a/3.0、QuickCommerce 2.5/3.0、Shop Express 1.0 及 StoreCreator 3.0 等版本，攻击无需身份认证，仅需构造特制 HTTP 请求即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0136"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:04.510","remediation":"对 Cart32 等购物车应用，升级至最新版本（Cart32 3.5a 及以上），确保所有价格、数量等敏感字段在服务端进行二次校验，禁止仅依赖前端隐藏表单字段传递数据。如无法升级，应通过服务端会话（Session）存储价格等关键信息，而非通过 HTML 隐藏域提交。同时部署 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）规则，拦截对隐藏表单字段的篡改请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0136","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19951","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/aa3114da1227373bef7855dba21bcaa5f0e0ad76/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0136.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0136","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/634779a1484dffc87947e325536a762c19a80895/2000/CVE-2000-0136.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0136.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2d